                          throws org.json.JSONException,
                                 java.text.ParseException,
                                 java.io.IOException,
                                 CaApiException
Perform an Event.Read.

Parameters:
dataBucket - The data bucket of the events
eventType - The type of events
start - The start time of the events (inclusive)
end - The end time of the events (inclusive)
pageSize - The maximum number of events to return in a single response
lastEvent - The lastEvent from the last Event.Read in order to query the next page of events.
lookup - Whether to perform Lookup.Read on all phone numbers from all returned events.
requestProfile - The request profile to use on lookups
Returns:
The event response
Throws:
org.json.JSONException - Error parsing JSON
java.text.ParseException - Error parsing the time of returned events
java.io.IOException - Error communicating with Caller Analytics API
CaApiException - Error processing API command
